      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLASHBACK JIM (1) has a strong winning strike-rate here with four wins and a placing from seven tries. Comes off a (26.10) win last time, scoring by 0.8 lengths in a Grade 5 over 457m at this track. Rates a leading player. MAKO MERV (7) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when second (22.78) over 400m at Dubbo. Leading player again. MAWONGA MAN (2) was below best at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth at this track, but was among the placings at this track three back. Can find the frame this time. LILLYVALE LAD (3) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage 0.8 lengths away in second (26.14). Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Well-placed to take this out.",
